      <title>马士基认为红海目前对其船舶来说太不安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/maersk-decides-the-red-sea-is-too-unsafe-for-its-ships-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[集装箱运输巨头 A.P. 穆勒-马士基公司表示，在其另一艘承运人在几周内遭受攻击后，该公司将再次停止让其船只穿越重要的贸易走廊红海。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/maersk-decides-the-red-sea-is-too-unsafe-for-its-ships-for-now</guid>
